n.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/Ng%E1%BB%A5-%C3%BD-ph%C3%A0m-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%A7-c%E1%BA%A3nh-th%E1%BA%BF-tam-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-968104YRF7-qQUg0a_6TAA">Ngụ ý phàm tứ thủ cảnh thế tam thủ kỳ 4 - 寓意凡四首警世三首其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C6%B0u-Th%C3%A1i-Xu%C3%A2n/poem-gQENlmz6YU4sqrECrtz5lQ">Tặng Lưu Thái Xuân - 贈劉采春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Th%C3%A1i-B%C3%ACnh-th%C3%A0nh-h%E1%BA%A1-v%C4%83n-xuy-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-P3_lyhyJZlihMSZWHrHVuA">Thái Bình thành hạ văn xuy địch - 太平城下聞吹笛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/T%C3%ADch-hoa/poem-OyPgnjg3EcvtCt6tBgYaXw">Tích hoa - 惜花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
